Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely get you there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die... Nami... Sanji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:18.24,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,103)\fsp-2)}The Island Where Snow Lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:18.24,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,405)}Climb The Drum Rockies!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Please look at that! \NWe found them, Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.21,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys're...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do many rude things to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll chew you guys up!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You're stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I get out of your way?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.69,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like what you have on your \Nback and in your arm are half-dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.79,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chess! I thought up a new law. \NWrite this down.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who ignore the king are to be executed!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignoring me already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.22,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! First, get the sick and injured ones, \Nwho are ignoring me the most!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.35,0:03:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yes sir! \N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the woman on his back!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the man.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! Marimo's Surprise!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.66,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you attack or get struck,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} will feel the whole impact too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.96,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph. What a coward...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show him...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what a battle in a snowy area is like...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they've already given up...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is a true battle in a snowy area!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The white disguise! \NSnow Powder Makeup!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.77,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they're so weak, \Nthey'll be dead with just one shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Mate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,White bears...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lapins?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they protect him?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.37,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a coincidence. \NLapins never become attached to humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! You saved me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do they think they're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find the doctor... up there...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there a little longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalanche...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We were swallowed by the avalanche...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! U... Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Hang on!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Vivi... Don't wake me up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just having a beautiful dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.90,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A field of beautiful flowers out of \Nthis world and a beautiful river... Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,– You're almost in the netherworld!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.65,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,– Isn't that Zoro swimming in the river...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wake up! Don't sleep! Wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.66,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All 74,000 Usopp Pirates, close in!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wake up! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NUsopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, you saved me, Vivi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about having a narrow escape from death.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm alive. But...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,– don't you think my face is kinda swollen?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– I-It's chilblains! Chilblains!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,– My head feels kinda heavy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,– This is why it's not easy to be in a snowy area.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,– Or should I say my view is kinda narrow...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,– More importantly,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– we have to figure out our location and the situation we're in quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– My lips are kinda big... Kinda...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yeah, I agree...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.74,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... That was close... \NI saw a field of flowers...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.62,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly hitting an avalanche in this cold... \NI must've run out of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a sort of winter swimming, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, Vivi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.22,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Usopp! \NWhat're you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you lowly bunnies \Nget for going against the king!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.28,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! I didn't think I'd use my \Nreal power on mere bunnies, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,since they're the most violent animal in Drum.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That... that was close...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter swimming?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NAfter swimming in the river for a while,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea where I was any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was walking while doing muscle training,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I ended up in a forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dressed like that? \NYou're stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, give me your coat, Usopp.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nami-{\i0}san{\i1} might've gotten sick \Ndue to mental exhaustion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,– Then your shoes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,– No!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,– {\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,– One of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there! There're people.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.87,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... I remember those buildings...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! This is Big Horn!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.47,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up... coming back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back! Step back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton is already dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.45,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0} \Nwould die from an attack like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys're Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}'s \Nex-subordinates, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're retainers of King Wapol!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s enemy, \Nyou're dead meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with {\i1}you{\i0}, dressing like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}'s buried under \Nthe snow of the avalanche!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0} is?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.64,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We can't dig him out \Nbecause those guys get in our way.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back! Step back!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any objection, \Ngo right ahead and bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, I remember their clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.73,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who attacked \Nus on the sea, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they're our enemy, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our enemy, right? What's the word? \NAre they on our side?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're our enemy... \Nbut why are you so...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't so courageous \Nwithout Dalton, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Mr. Bushido!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Stop it! \NIf you attack them, you'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is warm! I'm borrowing it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You... asked me because of that...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.91,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– Look! They're angry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– You!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the ship with that \Nguy who blew Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0} away!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You guys never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys looking for...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,these?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk Wave!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already over?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disappointing bunch...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Good job, Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I instructed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Dig everywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's all this fuss?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.15,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it later! Let's help them!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}! Please be alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there. We're almost there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you die on me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doktorin... \NThe antibodies are responding.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what's the cause? Explain.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kestia...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Kestia.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You attend the girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:10.43,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Nemuranai kono machi mo Ima dake wa madoromu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:17.02,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kyou kara to kinou made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:22.82,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}nani ka ga kawatte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:28.07,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kitto yarinaoseru hazu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:33.08,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Datte hitori janai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:38.25,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Soba ni ite kureru dake de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.59,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tsuyoku nareru ki ga suru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:48.84,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Doko made ikeru kana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:54.01,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}mirai e tsuzuku basho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:02.27,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Tooku de kagayaite sekai o tsutsumikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:06.03,ED5-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Yoake mae
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:10.43,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Even this sleepless town has dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:17.02,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}From today forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:22.82,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}something's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:28.07,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'm sure I can start fresh,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:33.08,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}since I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:38.25,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Just by having you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.59,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:48.84,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I wonder how far I can go,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:54.01,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}towards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:02.27,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Off in the distance it shines, encompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:06.03,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Before dawn
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.28,0:23:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, reindeer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NI'll cook a nutritious reindeer dish right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the food. \NI just want some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wasn't that reindeer speaking?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I sort of \Nremember him standing on two legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.25,0:23:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.47,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue-nosed Reindeer! \NChopper's Secret
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
